data.title: Aaron Fleetwood
data.meta_description: Posts about Aaron Fleetwood written by giantinthepaint
data.text: Aaron Fleetwood signed a contract with Pro Ballers Osnabrueck this weekend to join the Pro A team for the upcoming season. The 6’9″ forward returns to Osnabrueck after playing for Phoenix Hagen in the last two seasons. In his last year when Hagen played in the german BBL. He played 30 games averaging 14.8 mpg, 5.1 ppg and 3.1 rpg. His best performance in the german highest league was a very good performance against Ratiopharm Ulm where he posted a double double: 14 points and 10 rebounds. Aaron is well known by the Osnabrueck organization since he played there in his rookie season. With bringing in Fleetwood, Osnabrueck ads experience and athleticism to their team.
